    h1 Messages Component
    ul.docs-index
    p Messages React component represents <a href="../docs/messages.html">Messages</a> component.

    h2 Messages Components
    p There are following components included:
    ul
      li <code><b>Messages</b></code> / <code><b>F7Messages</b></code> - main Messages container
      li <code><b>Message</b></code> / <code><b>F7Message</b></code> - single message element
      li <code><b>MessagesTitle</b></code> / <code><b>F7MessagesTitle</b></code> - single messages title element

